org.openwms.common.comm.api

Class CommonMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openwms.common.comm.api.CommonMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ErrorMessage, RequestMessage, ResponseMessage

    public abstract class CommonMessage
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A CommonMessage is the abstract superclass of all messages sent to subsystems like PLC or ERP. A CommonMessage has always a message header and a body.
    Since:
    0.2
    Version:
    $Revision: $
    Author:
    Heiko Scherrer
